state.unicode: Produces excess food. The additional food of this province can support your other regions, provided that your faction's total food production is higher than the total food consumption.
Food consumption is higher than food production. If your faction has a food surplus then this settlement can import food to feed the populace; otherwise it will suffer from famine.
